title: #166 - Doug Stanhope, Greg Chaille, Chad Shank, & ME
description: Comedian Doug Stanhope, Greg Chaille, & Chad Shank (All Part of The Doug Stanhope Shotclog Podcast) & I hang out in Bisbee for one very drunken, gut laughing SWAPCAST...to be dead honest I don;t remember much of the evening so your guess is as good as mine...all I remember is that I laughed my ass off and it was a complete and total blast - Make sure to check out the last two episodes of Doug's Podcast b/c the plot thickens and shit gets interesting.
